    <text id="A9700T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>P. Brady writes to Alexander H. H. Stuart to help settle a financial dispute with
                    Daniel Brady.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient">Hon. Alex H. H. Stuart</name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1868-03-31">Mar 31/68</date>
                        <name type="place">Philad<hi rend="super">a</hi></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I beg to say that in Case <abbr expan="Daniel">Danl</abbr> Brady will carry out
                    his offer of Sep 3. <orig reg="Shortening">Shortning</orig> the last four
                    payments I will accept, giving him a full discharge from all further Claims,
                    returning him two notes of 2500 each and a release as <orig reg="Guardian"
                        >Guardine</orig> of my Children, he says the property of my Children passed
                    into my hands, not so. it went to pay the debts of P. Brady &amp; <abbr
                        expan="Company">Co.</abbr> after <hi rend="underline">I was</hi>
                    <orig reg="robbed">robed</orig>, I make the offer to accept his proposition now
                    as I am pressed by my <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> for monies due them <pb n="2"/>If you can
                    get 5000 in good bonds as the proposes in June so much the better I would prefer
                    an amicable settlement if it can <add hand="h1" place="inline">be</add> had on a
                    fair basis, and trust to him to <add hand="h1" place="inline">do</add> more when
                    he succeeds with his <orig reg="patent">pattent</orig>, it is understood thus he
                    is to pay your fees &amp; all charges <orig reg="incurred">incured</orig>
                    thus far</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours Very respectfully</salute>
                    <signed>P Brady</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
